[I] Library implementing a multi-purpose desktop calculator

[T] Qalculate! is a multi-purpose cross-platform desktop calculator. It is
[T] simple to use but provides power and versatility normally reserved for
[T] complicated math packages, as well as useful tools for everyday needs (such
[T] as currency conversion and percent calculation).

[U] https://qalculate.github.io/

